Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I overslept! I'm going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, my cute descendant. Don't forget you have\Naccess to something that makes you run faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! I forgot all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So once again, the day is saved\Nthanks to my Crisis Management form!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please write your name on this list of late arrivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you transform?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bring myself to do it in the middle of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:01:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magical Girl, Momo Chiyoda,\Nis obsessed with making me train in one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SCANNING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of mecha or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a body composition monitor for professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Muscle Mass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Segmental Muscle Mass\N{\an8}Left Arm\N{\an8}Low\N{\an8}Right Arm\N{\an8}Low\N{\an8}Core\N{\an8}Low\N{\an8}Overall - Low\N{\an8}Right Leg\NLow\N{\an8}Left Leg\NLow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like you've been able\Nto build much muscle lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here. I'm going to bring\Nmy special protein drink for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any special attacks of your own, Mikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, "Sunrise Arrow" and a few others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-th-that sounds so cool!\NI want to see! I want to see! I want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem just a little too excited about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, I've realized just how thrilling\Nthe idea of special attacks are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And unlike Momo, I get the feeling\Nyou might actually show me some of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So please let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me your special attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me! Show me! Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli. Protein powder. A variety of mysterious pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Strips of chicken meat warmed up by the Magical Girl\Nuntil they turn a strange color.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Her time beyond the fifth decimal place\Nis rounded for convivence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}SHAKE\N{\an9}SHAKE\N{\an8}SHAKE\N{\an8}SHAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This completes the specially made, pink protein shake\Ndesigned to help Shamiko's muscles grow fully!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gulp. Gulp. Gulp. Gulp. Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great! It goes down smooth\Nand tastes like it's really nutritious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'll make some more later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gulp. Gulp. Gulp. Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why exactly is it glowing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A THK Special\N{\an8}Simply Incredible\N{\an8}The Miraculous Human Body
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When humans push the muscle tissue\Nof their body to its absolute limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,their cells begin a new evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:02:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One more! One more! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's interesting. Hey, Shamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Dash\N{\an9}Dash\N{\an7}Dash\N{\an8}Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you weren't going to transform\Nin the middle of town?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt my life was in serious danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Demon Girl Next Door
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is shining too brightly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(I rubbed my eyes from the glare)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I took off without even thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,(It's time for us to spark the joy)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I hold back my swaying bangs with my left hand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,These familiar sights start to shine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,(Three, two, one)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to share our secret, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything is possible for us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,(Always stay by my side)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,(We trust each other)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,On that street corner we found a precious treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you went far away, I would definitely run after you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Our future is here, forever burning bright
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The fun is only just getting started
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(610,156)}The Ancestor Evolves!!\N{\an7}A Pair of Glasses Reflect Within a Dark Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shamiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Ogura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard all about it! You've been doing training lately\Nto become stronger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can make you immensely powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You want that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then it's decided. Just come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't agreed to anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we can finally have\Na close and personal chat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow me to my lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember this girl, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sion Ogura from Class C.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,According to what Anri told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogura is an oddball who is super\Ninto stuff like devils and magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always borrowing various rooms and equipment\Nin the school to do some very suspicious research.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She does a lot of weird stuff, but her grades are so good\Nthat the teachers all just put up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Looking for a home\N{\an8}THIS HAS BEEN RESOLVED\N{\an8}Please take this bird
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look at the scores\Nfrom the final exams that we just had...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}FINAL EXAMS: JULY - TOP SCORES\N{\an8}1st) Sion Ogura - 1190 points\N{\an8}2nd) Kumi Shirozaki - 1185 points\N{\an8}3rd) Lilith, the witch who governs over darkness - 1181 points
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in the top spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The only exam I didn't get 100% in was the ethics one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, it's all so far from the actual truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't comprehend why\Nthey marked me down in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I am Ruv - 1/2gauR = kTuv!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl is clearly lacking something\Nin the morals department.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she exactly the type of person we should avoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This reminds me, I think I remember seeing her\Nwatching Shamiko from the shadows pretty frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But the first time I was able to transform\Nwas after Ogura gave me an elixir to drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so she might actually be pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted\Nto get to know more about you, Shamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Demon Girl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'd be a perfect fit for my research!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us to become really close friends, Shamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I can do all sorts of experiments together with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound like the idea of friendship\Nthat I'm familiar with...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Black Magic\N{\an8}Studies Club
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,FWOOOSH!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where I've set up my lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You've got me with you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In the worst-case scenario,\Nwe'll just take whatever seems useful
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,then seal away all her memories of today\Nand make a run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really how a Magical Girl\Nshould be handling things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Without further ado, I welcome you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...to my lab, the Black Magic Studies Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}PANDORA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SEAL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo, put the wand away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get data by doing some experiments on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want to become stronger as a Demon Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That means our interests line up perfectly, no?\NIt's a great opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's gaze into the abyss together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Ogura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I get that you're enthusiastic to move things forward,\Nbut just calm down for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scaring Shamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Shamiko and I are working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't risk something bad happening\Nbecause of your weird experiments on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, I'm serving as Shamiko's producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to do anything to her,\Nthen you'll have to get my approval first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're serving as my what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have lots of ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For one, I want to expose her to an electric current\Nand gauge the quality of magic inside her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to draw her blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to transplant bat wings on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible. And none of these ideas are even acceptable\Nfrom an ethical standpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's three strikes, which means\Nyou're out and we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think Momo has any room to talk\Nconsidering what she does to Shamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be the Ancestor\Nwho I heard finally became able to speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyoda, do you mind if I do\Nsome demonic remodeling on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as it's nothing that can't be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to be inconspicuous\Nso she didn't find me, but my voice slipped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! Please leave my Ancestor alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, Shamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll agree to be her specimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, my feelings have started to change\Nsince I've been watching your progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find a way to escape the current cycle\Nof oppression we're stuck in with no way to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If these experiments can find a way to safely assure us\Na bright future, then I'll do whatever they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Drip...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Drip...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko, if I make it out of here alive, then please\Nmake me a hot bowl of udon when we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ancestor! All of your dialog is just making it seem\Nlike you're never going to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I promise not to do any experiments\Nthat leave irreparable harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}WHIRRRRR\N{\an8}WHIRRRRR
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That drill in your hand says otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SEAL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this statue is kind of like a router\Nthat connects our world
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to the sealed space that you currently reside in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can even control Shamiko through it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Although, that particular function\Nwas sealed off by the Magical Girl over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about I create a new vessel for you\Nto inherit and move around in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,C-can you actually make something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to try, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Producer Chiyoda, do you mind\Nif I ran an experiment like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not sure since Ms. Lilith\Nis one of the enemies who is after my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you agree to it, I'll include this mysterious elixir\Nthat makes Shamiko stronger at no extra cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So even Magical Girls are susceptible to bribery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is raw clay that's used to make homunculi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's some leftovers from another of my failed experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My theory is that since you and your ancestor\Nare blood relatives,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,if you infuse the clay with some of magic\Nto make arms and legs, then they'll work... maybe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let my Ancestor become mobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me Ancestor become mobile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, y-you know this clay has a really weird smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that would be because\Nthe base ingredient for homunculi is horse dung.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Horse dung?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how much farther can I fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE SOURCE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you some arms and legs, Ancestor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands are really sore from kneading that clay so\Nmuch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I stink so much it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Try standing up in your new form, Ancestor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard for me to move on just two legs!\NThe infused magic is too rough around the edges!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,H-how about if I try moving around on all fours like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like our experiment was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it's too weak to be a proper vessel,\Nso in a few minutes it will go back to being dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko, be straight with me. How do I look right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, you... you remind me of the cute\Neggplant cow decorations that we make for Obon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying to me, Shamiko. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be honest and tell me what you really think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I'm so clumsy and inexperienced\Nthat you ended up looking so freaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured that's how you felt. It's okay, Shamiko.\NYou did your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Lilith, after getting the gist of it,\NI made a little something for you from the leftover clay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed the clothes from something\Nthat was lying around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic is stronger than Shamiko's, so you should\Nbe able to control it remotely for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I created it by using Shamiko as a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot easier to control\Nthan that other body from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You look super cute, Ancestor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the sudden change of heart, Magical Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see a problem in letting you move freely\Nsince you don't really pose a threat either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Momo?\NDo you really want me to be mobile?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who sealed off the switch\Non my statue in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, if you infused this body with your magic,\Ndoesn't that drain it from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know you wanted a body to move around in,\Neven if it's just for a brief period.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it will last for very long,\Nbut I can make more for you occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can return the favor by agreeing to set\Na good example for Shamiko and help to train her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my deepest gratitude, Magical Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd ever say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just playing it friendly so you fall right\Ninto my trap! Thanks for being such a sucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it's only a limited time,\Nthere's now a chance for me to move freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret writing me off as "posing no threat"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You cocky little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I did let myself get a little emotional about it,\Nbut you're 5,000 years too young to be pitying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The time limit really sucks, but if I can just get Momo\Nto mass produce me a set of spare bodies then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"...when her guard is down, I'll make her bow\Nbefore me so that I can conquer the world!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the vibe your tail is giving off right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Lilith, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is happening?! My body is moving on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As I figured, it's also possible for me to control that body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}STIFF\N{\an8}STIFF\N{\an8}STIFF\N{\an8}STIFF
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Lilith, do a cute dance for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! I can't believe my own magic control\Non this body loses out to hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Look over this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko! You're on my side, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ancestor... your inner thoughts\Nwere openly conveyed through telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is mortifying... but my body can't help\Nbut groove to the rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's somehow making me start\Nto really enjoy all of this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think this means you've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Ancestor! By the way, if you get\Ninto a hot spring with that body it'll melt in a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Goddammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}YOSHIDA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Spin, spin, spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And then pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom has her very own point card\Nfor the Tama Sakura Shopping District!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Tama Sakura
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I already knew that, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But something good happened with it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Listen to this, Yuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}An elegant plate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I earn enough points,\NI can get a really elegant plate for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's quite elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Design
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, I would always go and get a free plate\Nwhenever I built up enough points for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,However, before I had enough time to get one\Nfor each member of our family, the design changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been upset\Nbecause I could never get a matching set.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It throws off the balance in the cupboard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why this time I waited until I had enough points\Nto exchange for three plates at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A perfect set of elegant plates
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one elegant set of elegant plates for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I'm headed out\Nto go exchange my points right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The laptop we borrowed from Ms. Momo\Nhas been acting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll start up, but after a few minutes it just stops working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a part of it broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know how computers work,\Nso let's go and ask Momo for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll apologize and see if she can fix it.\NIf it's broken, then I'll find a way to handl-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}HERE\N{\an8}LIES\N{\an8}LAPTOP
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko, I can't believe you'd destroy\None of my possessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today we'll be doing squats\Nwith a barbell instead of dumbbells.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}BUZZ\N{\an8}BUZZ\N{\an9}BUZZ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's absolutely nothing for you to worry about, Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis! Your tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Momo\N{\an8}Chiyoda
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! A fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just Momo's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wait here for a minute, Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already used to this routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I take the path of white stones\Nand clear it with no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good afternoon, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I get past the security\Nwith "Live Chicks n' Jive Tricks, Wahoo."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Demon Girl is on your doorstep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, Shamiko? Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}HIYAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I invite my little sister to come in right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo? Sure, feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted you to look at the laptop that we borrowed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're eating nothing\Nbut junk food for lunch again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let my eyes off you for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just lunch, does it really matter what I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Though if you're going to make me something, I'll eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not your personal Demon kitchen maid!\NBut fine, what type of food do you want to eat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse the intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo, I have a selfish request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to keep the fact\Nthat you're a Magical Girl secret from Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo believes that I'm a cool sister\Nwho is waging a war on Magical Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't find out that you actually\Nhave a grasp on all of my weaknesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}SHAKE SHAKE SHAKE\N{\an7}SHAKE SHAKE\N{\an8}Kelp Soup Stock\N{\an9}Sesame Oil
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even worse, that I come over\Nto your house to cook for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Or that I borrow your purse to go shopping for\Ningredients and even charge a point card in your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It might send her off the deep end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a point card in my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you earn points to get free stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko, didn't you tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Cooking Shamiko Style\N{\an7}Microwave frozen udon\N{\an7}for 3 minutes on high to defrost it.\N{\an7}For this dish, tuna is substituted\N{\an7}in place of the meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...that if you always live in fear\Nof other people seeing your weaknesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(954,240)}The base noodle stock is seasoned\N{\an8}with oyster sauce, sugar, and sake.\N{\an8}Shamiko style also calls for sesame oil\N{\an8}and some ginger paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,then you'll never be able to make any progress in life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but Ryo is my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I have to always set a good example\Nby being a strong sister who lives up to her ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Ms. Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this cute wand for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do this, and it makes\N{\an8}the food taste more delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wand meant for cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do this it makes the food taste more delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo's going all out to convince her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she washes that later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you had to go so far just to help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ask me, the one who suffers the most\Nis the person who keeps secrets from their loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The time hath come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This cat sounds like it can talk\Nand it shines like a lightbulb!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The time hath come! Time cometh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It cometh now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}JUST SAY NO!\N{\an8}TO WAND USE!\N{\an7}(Paid for by the Global Frying Pan Association)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not use Magical Girl wands\Nto stir ingredients in your frying pans at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that Momo is a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that we've been lying to you for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're working together right now for various reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:17:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew that you were lying\Njust to be considerate to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious from the way that Ms. Momo carries herself\Nthat she's trained as a military commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Military commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}WOOOOOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, Ms. Momo is a Magical Girl\Nwho joined the ranks of your army!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You used a dirty scheme not suitable to share\Nwith children to ensnare Ms. Momo into your army,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why you couldn't share\Nany of the details with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read about it before! I read lots of books like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so incredible that you made someone so strong\Ninto one of your subordinates without using force,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you've been coming to this fortress\Nto have strategy meetings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're even going out of your way to cook\Nfor your subordinate, that's so considerate Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing you in action really moved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit the nail on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me, how did you\Nbecome my sister's subordinate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mostly being attacked in my sleep,\Nand then having my fridge filled with delicious food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo is just sewing an even bigger web of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Momo! We were supposed to tell her the truth,\Nnot make things even more complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some smiles in the world\Nthat we have to protect... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be the unyielding one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought some ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who's this little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. She has absolutely no idea what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuko's little sister, Ryoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mikan, another Magical Girl\Nwho was called in to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you another member\Nof my sister's legion, Ms. Mikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Legion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that? The name of some new citrus fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikan... come with me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}POKE POKE POKE POKE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, don't touch me with the ice cream there!\NMy curse will act up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on,\Nbut I'll be a subordinate! I'll be a subordinate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ding...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now I am one of your loyal subordinates...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikan, I'll make it up to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(208,570)}The Magical Girls both enjoyed their ice cream after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Magical Girls both enjoyed their ice cream after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look. What do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The time hath come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo... I thought that older sisters\Naren't supposed to lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I think we should make sure\Nshe keeps that bright smile of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think Ryo's analysis of the situation\Nis that far from the truth, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't understand, then just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you for real? Can you really accept\Nbeing my subordinate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That look! You're really finding the idea hard to swallow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't find any problems with the laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have an A/C at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it just got overheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to only use it in the coolest room,\Nand if it gets hot, then let it take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come use it here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'm even more indebted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Shamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel that way, then make some more food for me\Nnext time you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the duties of a lord is making sure\Ntheir subordinates are well fed and healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Shadow Mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:20:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! It's not fair\Nif you say it when nobody's around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad that the laptop wasn't broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use it more carefully from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It has my journal, my private diary\Nand a lot of other important data!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you sure are using the laptop\Nto do a lot of different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I had Ms. Momo print them all out for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way more than any ordinary diary or journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ta-dah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She also taught me how important it is\Nto keep a variety of backups!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it, but I feel like\NI'm just piling up the debt at this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll study really hard and someday\Nbecome an advisor to your army!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}...I have to\N{\an7}do something\N{\an7}about this fantasy\N{\an7}of hers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do everything that I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...to someday make Ryo's fantasies come true\Nand find a way to surpass Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But how exactly can I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What I know about Momo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think about it, I still know very little about Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What I know about Momo\N{\an8}She likes noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Information about Momo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What I know about Momo\N{\an8}She likes noodles\N{\an7}She prefers soy sauce over regular sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Information about Momo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:21:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What I know about Momo\N{\an8}She likes noodles\N{\an7}She prefers soy sauce over regular sauce\N{\an8}She has nice handwriting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,About Momo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The only information I can think of\Nis absolutely worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to do some digging into Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling that she won't be willing\Nto tell me very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think she's keeping\Na lot of secrets on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply elegant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey Ryo.\N{\an8}I was really lonely today\N{\an8}because you guys\N{\an8}left me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Ryo. I was really lonely today\Nbecause you guys left me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As my future advisor there's something\NI'd like to ask you, Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had to seek out information about your enemy\Nand their weaknesses, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Find a way to get into their good graces\Nwithout being suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and then convince them to open up\Nand share with me... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it that way,\Nthen they'll naturally start to share their secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}My beloved sister\N{\an8}is far more technical\N{\an7}and much more advanced\N{\an7}than I would have ever thought...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My beloved sister is far more technical and much more\Nadvanced than I would have ever thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I should take her advice to heart and do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Ms. Momo put it in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Dear Ryo, This is a picture\N{\an7}of Shamiko's combat attire.\N{\an7}Please enjoy this immortalization\N{\an7}of her strength and bravery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Ryo, This is a picture of Shamiko's combat attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy this immortalization\Nof her strength and bravery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what you look like in battle, Sis.\NCan I take a few pictures of you some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Magical Girl! THIS MEANS WAR!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it looks really cool, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Shamiko! Become a Demon\Nwho exemplifies a cool lifestyle for your little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Demon Girl Next Door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gallantly, I demand a duel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I go at it, but I lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond disappointing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.45,0:22:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shift away from that grief
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I’m feeling curt
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll express myself with that tail
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a party in the neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the dogs are going bow-wow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Each and every last one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.75,0:22:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For all four seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When you fail just laugh it off
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Connecting our hearts like that time once before
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,With the miracle that we met in this town
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Grant this wish
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoulder those tires and go full throttle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.37,0:23:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning, there's still crises to manage, so enjoy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Various blooming colors are spilling off the canvas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,0:23:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now its sunset, don't bother thinking too much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, our compiled dreams can be any color
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.70,0:23:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's play some more
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:24:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ancestor, there's still so much about Momo,\Nthat I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch, I'm really going\Nto go all out from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.54,0:23:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! That's the spirit, Shamiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:24:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your magic has been slowly growing as of late,\Nso use it to give Momo a real surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And make it rhythmical!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Diving into Dreams Once Again!! Break Through the Pink Defense Line
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The time hath come!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the time has come
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to fully explain everything to Yuko.